 listings currently live for Lubbock. Fresh listings added weekly.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Indoor options</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">—</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Indoor options are being scouted—submit a favorite and we will feature it.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Lubbock<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Onsite services</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Indoor facilities</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Professional staff</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Climate controlled</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Parking available</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Easy access</span></span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad